            <p class="text-lg text-center text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">The new policies are gradually changing how people save, invest, and file their taxes. While adoption is growing, the reforms are also creating new challenges for traditional tax-saving products.</p>
             <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
