        <footer class="gradient-bg text-white rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl">
             <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Your Move: How to Choose Wisely</h2>
             <p class="text-lg text-center font-light max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">Navigating this dual-regime system requires a strategic approach. Here are key recommendations to ensure you make the most tax-efficient decision for your financial situation.</p>
